  "title": "Project & Technical Sales Engineer (Safety System)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position: </strong>Project & Technical Sales Engineer<br /><strong>Salary: </strong>$3600 to $7000 + Bonus<br /><strong>Working Days: </strong>Monday to Friday (9am-6pm)<br /><strong>Working Location: Kaki B</strong></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Possess Electrical Engineering educational qualification</li><li>Relevant working experience in Engineering & onboard vessel site services. </li><li>Knowledge of PAGA, CCTV, PABX, Fire Alarm Systems, Fire & Gas systems, Helideck lightings systems, Weather Monitoring systems, Aids to Navigation systems, Instruments, added advantage.</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities & Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Autocad Drawings and project documentation</li><li>Project administration and scheduling</li><li>Technical Sales proposal and clarifications with customers</li><li>Project engineering and design</li><li>Hands-on product integration , troubleshooting, testing, etc. </li><li>Site Services on board vessel (local & overseas)</li></ul><p>LIEW ONN KEE REG NO : R22108518</p><p>THE SUPREME HR ADVISORY EA NO:14C7279 </p>",
